node.text: I really enjoyed my conversation with @thecindygram, Editor-in-Chief of @interiordesignmag, on DesignBiz! Cindy and I discuss connecting to nature, a seamless transition between indoors and outdoors, and sustainability.

This is our skylark project in #westhollywood off #sunsetplaza  A great client and a wonderful collaboration with @mfullendesign and @gallobuildersinc #mondaymotivation #morning #summer #breeze #city #view #endless #vista #la #modern #glass #house #indooroutdoorliving

node.text: Renderings have become such an integral part of what we do. This one is for the ultimate fitness buff. A concept for a client a while back fit for any Olympic athlete that pushes the limits of what a gym can be that includes an indoor outdoor swimming pool, tilting walls a glass to take the work out outside,  a boxing ring as well as a climbing wall and all manner of weight racks and exercise machines. The only limit his imagination and how determined you are. Hope everyone has a much more restful Sunday, looking at this image is probably enough of a work out for the day😉 #fitness #goals #ultimate #gym #boxing #climbing #weights #running #swimming #indoor #outdoor #olympics

node.text: It’s been a long wait but these five projects are finally wrapping up and we hope to be taking photographs in the next two months of all of them. Can’t even list all the people who have helped us get them this far, really excited to be sharing a lot of new work finally. It’s been slow finishing things through Covid but we finally are getting there  talk about #mondaymotivation. node.text: A different view of the same project from yesterday showing how the fire pit area sits in the water underneath the glass entry bridge and looking through to the view of the city below through whats actually a basement. We try very hard to bring light into lower levels our homes so that nobody feels like they’re below grade at all. Part of the key to making this work is to find different sources of light from different directions #new #project #design #modern #architecture #ideas #city #view #lights #water #bridge #firepit
